OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FManchester City have confirmed that
OL,8,FPep Guardiola will leave the club
OL,9,Fafter ten years in charge.
OL,11,FHis decade-long reign at City is one
OL,12,Fof the most successful managerial
OL,13,Fspells in English football history,
OL,14,Fhaving won 20 trophies, including six
OL,15,FPremier League titles and the
OL,16,FChampions League.
OL,18,FHere's a look at some of Guardiola's
OL,19,Fmost defining moments:
OL,21,FSelling Joe Hart (Summer 2016)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
