OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FGuardiola decided immediately that
OL,8,FHart, the England number one, a two-
OL,9,Ftime Premier League winner, was not
OL,10,Fgood enough with his feet for his
OL,11,Fstyle. It was a ruthless call,
OL,12,Fquestioned when replacement Claudio
OL,13,FBravo struggled, but the arrival of
OL,14,FEderson the following year brought
OL,15,Fvindication.
OL,17,FNapoli statement (October-November
OL,18,F2017)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
