OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FAfter an indifferent first season,
OL,8,FGuardiola's City made a Champions
OL,9,FLeague statement with back-to-back
OL,10,Fwins over a much-vaunted Napoli side.
OL,11,FGuardiola described Maurizio Sarri's
OL,12,Fteam as one of the best he had faced,
OL,13,Fbut City won 2-1 at the Etihad and 4-2
OL,14,Fin Italy. It was the moment they
OL,15,Fgained wider European credibility.
OL,17,FDecisive Derby (December 2017)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
