OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FScepticism from Guardiola's first
OL,8,Fseason faded as City moved 11 points
OL,9,Fclear with a 2-1 win over Manchester
OL,10,FUnited at Old Trafford. United boss
OL,11,FJose Mourinho complained, but City
OL,12,Fwere dominant and the title race was
OL,13,Feffectively over.
OL,15,FCenturions and record-breakers (April-
OL,16,FMay 2018)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
