OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FCity were not playing when their first
OL,8,Ftitle under Guardiola was confirmed as
OL,9,FWest Brom beat United, sparking
OL,10,Fimpromptu celebrations from the
OL,11,Fplayers in a local pub. They quickly
OL,12,Frefocused, finishing with 100 points,
OL,13,F32 wins, 106 goals and a 19-point
OL,14,Fmargin ` all records.
OL,16,FMagic from Stones and Kompany (2018-19)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
