OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FCity edged Liverpool 98 points to 97
OL,8,Fin a remarkable title race. John
OL,9,FStones' 11mm goal-line clearance
OL,10,Fpreserved a 2-1 win over Jurgen
OL,11,FKlopp's Reds, while Vincent Kompany's
OL,12,Flate strike against Leicester
OL,13,Fultimately kept them ahead.
OL,15,FWatford rout (May 2019)
OL,17,FA 6-0 FA Cup final win over Watford
OL,18,Fsealed English men's football's first
OL,19,Fdomestic treble and was the biggest
OL,20,Fwinning margin in the fixture since
OL,21,F1903, underlining City's dominance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
