OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FTactical reinvention (2020-21 & 2021-
OL,8,F22)
OL,10,FFirst prompted by injury to Sergio
OL,11,FAguero, and then the Argentinian's
OL,12,Fdeparture ` plus a failed move for
OL,13,FHarry Kane ` Guardiola reshaped City
OL,14,Faround a false nine. It brought more
OL,15,Fleague titles in 2021 and 2022, when
OL,16,Fthey recovered from 2-0 down against
OL,17,FAston Villa on the final day to pip
OL,18,FLiverpool again.
OL,20,FReaching first Champions League final
OL,21,F(2021)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
