OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FAfter years of near-misses, City
OL,8,Freached their first final by sweeping
OL,9,Faside Paris St Germain 4-1 on
OL,10,Faggregate. Defeat followed, but it
OL,11,Fmarked a breakthrough.
OL,13,FThrashing Real Madrid (2023)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
