PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779455475
OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FIn arguably Guardiola's finest City
OL,8,Fperformance, his side beat Real Madrid
OL,9,F4-0 to reach the final. Bernardo Silva
OL,10,Fstruck twice before further goals from
OL,11,FManuel Akanji and Julian Alvarez
OL,12,Fsealed a 5-1 aggregate win. It was
OL,13,Fruthless and emphatic, and a major
OL,14,Fpsychological barrier had been broken.
OL,16,FKings of Europe (2023)
OL,18,FRodri's goal secured a 1-0 win over
OL,19,FInter Milan in Istanbul, completing a
OL,20,Fglorious treble and removing the final
OL,21,Fdoubt over Guardiola's time in England.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
