OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FOrtega save (2024)
OL,9,FSubstitute goalkeeper Stefan Ortega
OL,10,Fproduced a crucial late save to deny
OL,11,FSon Heung-min and effectively secure a
OL,12,Ffourth successive title. His 86th-
OL,13,Fminute stop, with City 1-0 up at
OL,14,FTottenham, was followed by a second
OL,15,Fgoal from Erling Haaland. Had Son
OL,16,Fscored, Arsenal would have gone into
OL,17,Fthe final day top.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
