OL,3,CPep Guardiola's memorable moments:
OL,4,CFrom selling Joe Hart to conquering
OL,5,CEurope
OL,7,FArguably there should have been more
OL,8,FEuropean glory, but Guardiola's decade
OL,9,Fat City has still seen plenty of
OL,10,Fsuccess and will be remembered for far
OL,11,Fmore than trophies and records. He not
OL,12,Fonly mastered English football, but
OL,13,Ftransformed it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
